msgid "Shadow Bacon"
msgid_plural "Shadow Bacons"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Shadow Bacon'}
#: .\essencelike_items.json
msgid ""
"This is no ordinary bacon, this is SHADOW bacon! A rare delicacy, almost "
"unheard of. It looks so amazing you feel unworthy being in it's presence, "
"much less eating it. So instead, you can honor this fabled bacon by turning "
"into freaking awesome gear! Either that or just sit it to collect dust on a "
"shelf in you bunker. That would work too."
msgstr ""

